trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The DataKeyArray class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DataKeyArray brukes til å lagre og behandle en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> object represents the primary key of a record in a data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey>objektet representerer primærnøkkel for en oppføring i en databundet-kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey>

trans-unit.source: In general, data-bound controls that display multiple records (such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control) use a DataKeyArray object to store the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> objects for the records displayed in the control.
trans-unit.target: Generelt databundet kontrollerer som viser flere poster (som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen) bruker en DataKeyArray-objektet til å lagre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey>objekter for oppføringene vises i kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The DataKeyArray class supports several ways to access the items in the collection: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.Item%2A> indexer to directly retrieve a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> object from the collection at a specific zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DataKeyArray støtter flere metoder for å få tilgang til elementer i samlingen:-Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.Item%2A>indekserer til å hente direkte en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey>objektet fra samlingen i et bestemt nullbaserte indeksen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.GetEnumerator%2A> method to retrieve an enumerator that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.GetEnumerator%2A>metode for å hente en opplisting som kan brukes til å gå gjennom samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.GetEnumerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.CopyTo%2A> method to copy the items in the collection into an array, which can then be used to access the items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.CopyTo%2A>metode for å kopiere elementene i samlingen til en matrise, som kan brukes til å få tilgang til elementer i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: To determine the total number of items in the collection, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.Count%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Bruk til å fastslå antall elementer i samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.Count%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray> class using the specified <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å initialisere en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray>klasse parametersettet med de angitte <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>objektet.</xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyArray>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> object contains the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> objects with which to populate the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>objektet inneholder den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey>objekter som å fylle ut samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey> </xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"></xref> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"></xref> objects with which to populate the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"> </xref> av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"> </xref> objekter som å fylle ut samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies all the items from this collection to the specified array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"></xref> objects, starting at the specified index in the array.
trans-unit.target: Kopierer alle elementene fra denne samlingen til den angitte matrisen for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"> </xref> objekter, med Start fra den angitte indeksen i matrisen.

trans-unit.source: Use the CopyTo method to copy the items from the collection into the specified array, starting at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Bruk CopyTo-metoden til å kopiere elementene fra samlingen i den angitte matrisen, med Start fra den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: The array can then be used to access the items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Matrisen kan deretter brukes til å få tilgang til elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > You must use a zero-based array for the `array` parameter.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Må du bruke en nullbasert matrise for den `array` parameteren.

trans-unit.source: A zero-based array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"></xref> objects that receives the copied items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: En nullbasert matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"> </xref> objekter som mottar kopierte elementer fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The first index in the specified array to receive the copied contents.
trans-unit.target: Den første indeksen i den angitte matrisen til å motta kopierte innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter antallet elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use the Count property to determine the number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk Count-egenskapen til å finne ut hvor mange elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Count property is commonly used when iterating through the collection to determine its upper bound.
trans-unit.target: Count-egenskapen brukes vanligvis under gjentakelse samlingen til å finne den øvre grensen.

trans-unit.source: The Count property is also commonly used to determine whether a collection is empty.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen antall brukes også vanligvis til å finne ut om en samling er tom.

trans-unit.source: The number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Antall elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.target: Returnerer en opplisting som inneholder alle <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"> </xref> objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use the GetEnumerator method to get an enumerator that can be iterated through linearly to access each item in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk GetEnumerator-metode for å få en opplisting som kan være iterated via lineært å få tilgang til hvert element i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: To access the item at the current position in the enumerator, use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha tilgang til elementet ved gjeldende plassering i enumeratoren, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move to the next item in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte til neste element i samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To move the enumerator to its initial position, use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: For å flytte enumeratoren til den opprinnelige posisjonen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When you initially get the enumerator or use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator to the first item in the collection, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når du først få enumeratoren eller bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte enumeratoren til det første elementet i samlingen du må kalle den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the item represented by the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Ellers elementet som representerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen er ikke definert.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-implemented object that contains all <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKey"></xref> objects in the collection.
